Title: 'Go deeper inside myself '
DateModified: '2019-03-05'
DatePublished: '2019-03-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/go-deeper-inside-myself
SetInCountry: France
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: "C\xE9line Bance"
AuthorCountry: France
Text: This is the story of a mad woman that was so deeply and emotionally sad ; she
  didn't know what to do in her life so she decided to go futher than herself, explore
  others countries in Europe. Into a beautiful, green place in Netherland, to the
  Wonderland country, she learnt how to become more confident by going on stage during
  an awesome project, she sang, danced, performed as never. She learnt how to be more
  patient in life and how to be reflected not thinking too much, doing what she loved
  to do and be passionated by what she do. Outgoing crazy woman, she never give up,
  she always went deeply. She met different people that allowed her to become more
  open to the others, going out of her comfort zone without never be ashamed to fail
  or fall down on the floor. This shinny, sparkling girl knowing her better than before
  and she is proud of herself. This is what this woman want to teach to others, be
  passionated no matter what and doing what you dream of to do, or sharing. Be yourself,
  healthy in your mind and body, in good health.
